casebody.data:
GREEN EMERALD HOMES, LLC., Appellant,
v.
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, as Trustee FOR CREDIT SUISSE FIRST BOSTON MORTGAGE SECURITIES CORP., CSAB Mortgage-Backed Pass through Certificates, Series 2006-3, Maria A. Adorno, et al., Appellees. Case No. 5D18-0299 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fifth District. Opinion filed June 22, 2018 Robin I. Frank, of Shapiro, Blasi, Wasserman & Hermann, P.A., Boca Raton, for Appellant. Maureen B. Walsh, Sara F. Holladay-Tobias, Emily Y. Rottmann, of McGuirewoods LLP, Jacksonville, for Appellee, U.S. Bank National Association. No Appearance for other Appellees. ON CONFESSION OF ERROR PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to Appellee's Confession of Error, we reverse the trial court's January 4, 2018 Order to Make Payments and remand this matter to the trial court for further proceedings.

REVERSED and REMANDED.

WALLIS, LAMBERT, AND EDWARDS, JJ., concur.
